      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=lv83oe1dk2]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=lv83oe1dk2]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=auqw680lqi]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=auqw680lqi]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=dh0edkrqct]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=dh0edkrqct]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=zd1cpohy6m]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=zd1cpohy6m]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=b4nmzlnn1t]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=b4nmzlnn1t]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=clwc1uqxs0]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=clwc1uqxs0]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=kz7w3do0ed]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=kz7w3do0ed]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RU_DeskBadge2.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599261185/RU_DeskBadge2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762449667903&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599261185/RU_DeskBadge2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762449667903&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"651952149\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RU_DeskBadge2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599261185\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"25\