width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606699548\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"kickstarter_banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599261185\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"25\" data-media-id=\"d91d8e8b-d56a-42fe-b434-e4bf272e1765\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599261185/kickstarter_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758207383869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599261185/kickstarter_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758207383869&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"NewtoRenderMan?-RenderManKickstarters\"><span data-colorid=\"auqw680lqi\">RenderMan Kickstarters</span></h1><p>A set of DCC-specific Kickstarter lessons to get you up and rendering in no time.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/599162914/RenderMan+Fundamentals\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599162914\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"fundamentals_banner.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599261185/fundamentals_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758206381290&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599261185/fundamentals_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758206381290&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606863367\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"fundamentals_banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599261185\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"25\" data-media-id=\"955204bd-1190-4094-bd2e-469234972ccf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599261185/fundamentals_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758206381290&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599261185/fundamentals_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758206381290&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"NewtoRenderMan?-RenderManFundamentals\"><span data-colorid=\"clwc1uqxs0\">RenderMan </span><br /><span data-colorid=\"b4nmzlnn1t\">Fundamentals</span></h1><p>Our comprehensive video-based learning series on the fundamentals of RenderMan</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/608632849/Introduction+to+Best+Practices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608632849\" data-linked-resource-version=\"16\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" 